---
// Layout Landing Page Minimalis - Apple HIG Inspired
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Orca: Landing Page</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #000000;
            --text: #f5f5f7;
            --text-dim: #86868b;
            --accent: #2997ff;
            --surface: #1d1d1f;
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(41, 151, 255, 0.1);
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(41, 151, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(41, 151, 255, 0.4);
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <span class="badge">Astro & Bun Integration</span>
        <h1>Orca</h1>
        <p>Landing page modular performa tinggi, dirancang untuk efisiensi kecepatan rendering maksimum.</p>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button">Pelajari Lebih Lanjut</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
